description._content: Description: View in January 1929 of the same two terraces as No. 56, Elevation about 4,000 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: January 1929 Description: View in 1921 of Aleppo Pine on the Northern slope, between Kannavia and Yerokamina Valleys, about 45 years old, Adelphi Forest, Elevation 1,800 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1921 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
